OL,3,CDispersal order in place for Carlisle
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,FCumbria Constabulary has issued a
OL,7,Fdispersal order for Carlisle on 10
OL,8,FAugust 2024.
OL,10,FIt follows an order which was in place
OL,11,Fon Wednesday to help officers maintain
OL,12,Forder in the city.
OL,14,FThese powers will be used again on
OL,15,FSaturday and the dispersal order will
OL,16,Fbe in place from 10am on Saturday
OL,17,Funtil midnight.
OL,19,FThe public should expect to see an
OL,20,Fincreased police presence throughout
OL,21,Fthe day.
