OL,3,CDispersal order in place for Carlisle
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,FAdditional powers have been put in
OL,7,Fplace to provide officers with
OL,8,Fenhanced stop and search capabilities.
OL,10,FOfficers will also have the authority
OL,11,Fto order the removal of face coverings
OL,12,Fif they beleive it is being used to
OL,13,Fdisguise or conceal a person's
OL,14,Fappearance.
OL,16,FOfficers will also have the power to
OL,17,Fseize any item used to commit anti-
OL,18,Fsocial behaviour.
