OL,3,CDispersal order in place for Carlisle
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,FChief Superintendent Carl Patrick
OL,7,Fsaid: "The dispersal order and
OL,8,Fadditional powers will ensure officers
OL,9,Fon the streets have the authorisation
OL,10,Fto act swiftly if confronted by groups
OL,11,For individuals intent on engaging in
OL,12,Fviolent disorder.
OL,14,F"Public safety is our number one
OL,15,Fpriority and officers on the ground
OL,16,Fwill work to ensure that the law-
OL,17,Fabiding majority of people are free to
OL,18,Fgo about their business in the city
OL,19,Fwithout fear.
