OL,3,CDispersal order in place for Carlisle
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,F"Whilst we will continue to support
OL,7,Fand facilitate the right to peaceful
OL,8,Fprotest, our message to anyone
OL,9,Fintending to engage in disorder is to
OL,10,Fstay away.
OL,12,F"Officers will respond swiftly and
OL,13,Fdecisively to any individuals who
OL,14,Fengage in criminality."
OL,16,FAcross Cumbria there will be
OL,17,Fadditional officers providing an
OL,18,Fincreased policing presence, engaging
OL,19,Fwith communities and providing
OL,20,Freassurance.
